-- Fase 2 - Producción --
[Motor de diálogo] as [MOTOR] starts at [M1]'s end lasts 8 days #prod-code
[Sistema variables] as [VAR] lasts 4 days after [MOTOR] #prod-code
[Sistema guardado] as [SAVE] lasts 4 days after [VAR] #prod-code
[Implementación escenas] as [ESC] lasts 6 days after [SAVE] #prod-code

[Fondos urbanos] as [FOND] starts at [ART]'s end lasts 15 days #prod-art
[Sprites personajes] as [SPR] lasts 12 days after [FOND] #prod-art

[Música y SFX] as [SFX] starts at [ART]'s end lasts 12 days #prod-art

[Integración] as [INT] lasts 12 days after [SPR] and [SFX] #prod-code
[Rutas alternativas] as [RALT] lasts 10 days after [INT] #prod-code
[Pruebas internas] as [TEST] lasts 6 days after [RALT] #prod-code

' Milestone 2
[M2] happens at [TEST]'s end #milestone
note bottom of [M2]
  Beta completa
end note

-- Fase 3 - Postproducción --
