[Ajustes narrativos] as [ADJ] lasts 3 days after [QA] #postprod
[Títulos y créditos] as [CRED] lasts 2 days after [ADJ] #postprod
[Optimización] as [OPT] lasts 3 days after [CRED] #postprod
[Marketing] as [MKT] lasts 4 days after [ADJ] #postprod
[Publicación] as [PUB] lasts 2 days after [OPT] and [MKT] #postprod

